fr.ign.cogit.cartagen.software.dataset

Class CartAGenDocOld

  • Object
    • CartAGenDocOld
  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class CartAGenDocOld
extends Object
    this class represents work documents in CartAGen, as .mxd files in ArcGIS or .got files in Clarity. The document has information on the area of imported data and is related to the CartAGenDatabase objects opened. It also refers to the PostGIS DB used to store persistently data within the document.
    Author:
    Guillaume
